## Project Info 

1. N-Tier Architecture
2. C# ASP.NET Core 6 (Jwt, Swagger, NLog)
3. MS SQL (mdf) DB for data storage - in the folder API/App_Data - (EntityFrameworkCore, Code First, Faker.Net)
4. ASP.NET Core MVC (Razor) for front end (MVC, Razor, RestSharp)
